Antergos Linux - Godot v2.2 alpha_build

When adding a 0.0000001 to any number, the resulting print, will be the same number.

```
func _ready():
    var a = Vector3(0,0,0)
    var b = Vector3(0,0,0)
    a += Vector3(0.0000001, 0.0000001, 0.0000001)
    printt(a, b, a != b)
    printt(1 + 0.0000001)
```
